[Intro]

[G] [C/G] [G] [C/G]

[G][C/G][Verse [G][C/G]1]

[G]Why are there [Em]so many [C]songs about [D]rainbows,

and [G]what's on the [Em]other [C][D]side?

[G]Rainbows are [Em]visions, [C]but only [D]illusions.

[G]Rainbows have [Em]nothing to [C]hide.

