[Cmaj7]So we've been told and some choose to believe it.

[Bm7]I know they're wrong; wait and see.

[Chorus]

[Am]Some day we'll [D]find it, the [Bm7]rainbow [E]connection,

[Am]The lovers, the [D]dreamers, and [G]me.

[Interlude]

[G][C/G][Verse [G][C/G]2]

